<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />But, when they were sick, I wore sackcloth;</para>

<para style="q1">I fasted for them</para>

<para style="q1">with my head bowed on my chest.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="14" style="v" />I went about in grief as for my brother;</para>

<para style="q1">I bent down in mourning as for my mother.</para>
